title: 109_hr1948
content: Directs the Bureau of Customs and Border Protection to: (1) reliquidate certain entries of aquascape relaxation bubble lights. (2) make such reliquidation at the rate of duty that would have been applicable to such merchandise if it had been liquidated under a specified subheading of the Harmonized Tariff Schedule of the United States on its date of entry, and (3) refund any amounts owed with interest.
